\newlabel{tab:topology_transfer}{{III}{5}{Cross-topology IEE transfer benchmark ($n=100$, $N_\mathrm {train}=10$, $N_\mathrm {test}=20$ seeds per topology). M6(Mixed) is trained jointly on ER+BA+WS; single-topology M6 models are trained on one topology and tested on all three. Worst-case $= \max _\mathrm {topo}$~IEE; Topo-Var $= \sigma $~of per-topo means; TTHM $=$ time to half mass (lower $=$ faster deletion). Bold $=$ best per column. M6(Mixed) wins on Worst-case, Topo-Var, CV, and TTHM}{table.3}{}}
