\newlabel{tab:welch_tests}{{V}{5}{Welch two-sample $t$-tests comparing M5 (Social threshold) against M6 ensemble variants across topologies ($n=100$, $N=50$ seeds). Bonferroni correction applied for 6 simultaneous comparisons. Cohen's $d$ measures standardised effect size (positive = M5 $>$ M6, i.e.\ M6 reduces IEE). $^{***}$: $p<0.001$; $^{**}$: $p<0.01$; $^{*}$: $p<0.05$}{table.5}{}}
